---
title: Double Caribbean Chicken Strips & Coconut Sauce with Charred Pineapple Slaw & Crushed Peanuts
description: Eat the tropical rainbow tonight with this vibrant collection of veggies and chicken strips cooked in our mild
Caribbean jerk seasoning. We’re keeping those beach vibes going by adding a charred pineapple slaw, coconut
sauce and a hint of nutty peanuts.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
